\b0\fs22 Hello and welcome to this very first version of MilkyTracker a platform independent FastTracker II "clone"\par
\par
Currently supported platforms are:\par
- Windows\par
- Mac OS X\par
- PocketPC (Windows CE 3.0 and above)\par
\par
I'm also working on a pure SDL port which is supposed to run under Linux as well but it will take some more time.\par
\par
