\ul\b\fs24 Quick Overview:\par
\ulnone\b0\fs22\par
Due to request MilkyTracker features two edit modes:\par
\par
\ul\b I. MilkyTracker edit mode:\b0\par
\ulnone The MilkyTracker mode basically a bit more "modern" because you can focus on different parts \par
(e.g. Pattern Editor, Instrument Listbox, Sample Listbox etc.) and when you're pressing\par
keys they're routed to the focused control.\par
Also keyboard shortcuts are more standard, you can select by pressing the SHIFT key\par
and navigating with the cursor keys, cut, copy & paste with using CTRL+X/C/V etc.\par
I think users who are new to tracking will find this a bit more intuitive.\par
The edit mode can be changed in the config screen (Misc. tab)\par
\par
